column13: Cells were cultured adherently under neural stem cell conditions.
column15: Libraries were constructed as described in Buenrostro et al., Nature Methods, (2013).
column17: Libraries were sequenced with 50 bp single-end reads which were mapped to hg19 using bowtie2. Reads were filtered to remove duplicates, unmapped or poor quality (Q <30) reads, mitochondrial reads, chrY reads, and those overlapping the ENCODE blacklist., The signal intensity featured in the bedgraph files was calculated as the fold enrichment of the signal per million reads in a sample over a modelled local background using the bdgcmp function in MACS2.
column41: *_sortedFE.bedgraph: bedGraph; signal file produced with MACS2 as described above.
